{
  "message": "fuzz(datetime_parsing): extend corpus with 22 edge-case seeds\n\nAdds coverage for:\n- Leap year dates (2024-02-29 valid, 2023-02-29 invalid)\n- Ordinal dates (2024-366, 2024-001)\n- Week dates (2024W01, 2024-W53)\n- Edge times (24:00:00, 23:59:60 leap second)\n- Duration edge cases (P1W, PT0S, P0D, -P1D)\n- Boundary dates (9999-12-31, 0000-01-01, -0001-01-01)\n- Nanosecond precision timestamps\n- Relative date strings (now, today)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
